I just found out that Patrick from Spongebob's name in Korean Spongebob&nbsp; Squarepants is &quot;Dalmoni.&quot; 

And Sandy the Squirell's name is &quot;Space Girl.&quot; 

Gary also has a different name - I forget what. 

Plankton is plain-old &quot;Plankton.&quot; 

The kids pronounce Spongebob as &quot;SpongEE Bob-UH.&quot;&nbsp;Mr. Crabs is &quot;MistUH CrabsUH.&quot;&nbsp;

Source: My 2nd-graders who are obsessed with Spongebob.

